{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on your Grandpa's old shop and fix up your customer's treasured belongings. From bells to binoculars and toys to teapots, each forest friend will have something new for you to repair!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Open up your old family shop and bring it back to life by taking on work from woodland friends like Mr Cotton the Rabbit, Chef Bastien the Capybara and Dash the Sparrow! Help fix, paint and clean their most treasured belongings to put your shop back on the map, play some Bear Fish Bee to climb the village leaderboard, and get your shop clean and repaired in this <strong>new demo!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468410/extras/steamgif2.gif?t=1740583626\" />:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Piece together antiques, heirlooms, and favourite mugs for your customers, each with its own puzzle! Re-assemble the pieces into their correct spaces by turning and twisting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grab your colourful paints, and paint up a storm before selling them for a profit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep your shop in check by cleaning up the floor and entering the Bear Fish Bee league!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make your shop your own by picking out furniture, rugs and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play the first hour, from fixing up your shop's sign to getting your oven back up and working!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468410/extras/steamgif1.gif?t=1740583626\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3468410?t=1740583626","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackgro